snippet.title: Vinebound: Bloom & Boom - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Vinebound: Bloom & Boom is a tasty mix of horde-survival roguelite and chaotic couch co-op for 1-2 players. Coordinate your position, synchronize attacks, and defeat hordes of moldy foes while unlocking new arsenals to cultivate plantastic builds.

Wishlist now on Steam!
